&lt;Canamax Resources Inc> said it agreedto acquire the 50 pct interest it does not already own in theKrezmar gold property, near Wawa, Ontario, by paying nine mlndlrs to &lt;Algoma Steel Corp Ltd> and granting Algoma a four pctnet smelter return royalty, which is payable after payback.    The property's drill indicated reserves to a depth of 1,200feet are estimated at over one mln tons averaging 0.25 ouncesof gold a ton, Canamax said. Reuter&#3;